text:
('Der deutsche Bundesminister f√ºr Wirtschaft und Klimaschutz, Robert Habeck, erkl√§rte am Montag auf dem Weltwirtschaftsforum in Davos, dass eine Aufhebung der Sanktionen gegen Russland ausgeschlossen sei, selbst wenn dies den Verlust von 100.000 Menschenleben bedeute.

Angesichts der sich versch√§rfenden Hungerkrise, die durch die Blockade des Schwarzmeer-Handels weiter verst√§rkt wird, spricht sich Habeck dennoch gegen die Aufnahme von Verhandlungen mit Russland aus. Laut dem UN-Weltern√§hrungsprogramm besteht die Gefahr einer gro√üen Hungersnot und steigender Lebensmittelpreise weltweit

Diese Aussagen m√∂gen an ein inzwischen legend√§res Interview (1996) der ehemaligen US-Au√üenministerin Madeleine Albright zu den US-Sanktionen gegen den Irak erinnern. Darin erkl√§rte Albright, dass das Sterben von mehr als einer halben Million irakischer Kinder ihren Preis wert waren.

Weltwirtschaftsforum in Davos I 23.05.2022

#RobertHabeck', "At the World Economic Forum in Davos on Monday, Germany's Minister for Economic Affairs and Climate Protection, Robert Habeck, said that sanctions against Russia could not be lifted, even if it meant the loss of 100,000 lives.

In view of the worsening hunger crisis, which is being exacerbated by the blockade of Black Sea trade, Habeck is nonetheless opposed to opening negotiations with Russia. According to the UN World Food Program, there is a risk of major famine and rising food prices worldwide

These statements may be reminiscent of a now legendary interview (1996) by former US Secretary of State Madeleine Albright on US sanctions against Iraq. In it, Albright declared that the deaths of more than half a million Iraqi children were worth their price.

World Economic Forum in Davos I May 23, 2022

contents
The UK government admits that vaccines damaged the natural immune system in two ways
vaccinated
The UK government has admitted that double vaccination will never be able to be obtained again
full natural resistance to Covid- variants or possibly to any other virus
So let's see how the real pandemic starts!
In its COVID-19 Vaccine Monitoring Report In Week 42, the UK
Health admits on page 23 that levels of N antibodies appear to be lower in those infected
after two doses of the vaccine He also finds that this decline in antibodies is essentially permanent
What does it mean?
We know that vaccines do not prevent infection or transmission of the virus (in fact, report
shows elsewhere that vaccinated adults are now infected much more often than
people who are not infected).
The British are now discovering that the vaccine affects the body's ability to produce
antibodies not only against the protein spikes, but also against other parts of the virus after infection.
In particular, vaccinated people do not appear to develop antibodies to the protein
nucleocapsid, the viral envelope that is a key part of the response in unvaccinated people.
In the long run, vaccinated people are much more susceptible to possible mutations in
spiked protein, even if they have already been infected and treated once or several times.
On the other hand, unvaccinated people will gain permanent, if not permanent, immunity to all strains
the alleged virus after being naturally infected with it at least once.

The British government admits that the vaccines damaged the natural immune system of people who were vaccinated twice.
The UK government has admitted that, after double vaccination, you will never be able to acquire full natural immunity to variants of the Covid virus - or possibly any other virus.
So let's watch the "real" pandemic begin!
In its Week 42 "COVID-19 Vaccine Surveillance Report", the UK Department of Health admits on page 23 that "N antibody levels appear to be lower in people who become infected after two doses of the vaccine."
It is further said that this decrease in antibodies is essentially constant.
What does it mean?
We know that vaccines do not prevent infection or transmission of the virus (in fact, elsewhere in the report it has been shown that
that vaccinated adults are now much more likely to become infected than unvaccinated adults).
The British have now found that the vaccine interferes with the body's ability to produce antibodies after infection not only against the spike protein, but also against other parts of the virus.
In particular, vaccinated people do not appear to develop antibodies to the nucleocapsid protein, the viral envelope, which is a key part of the response in unvaccinated individuals.
In the long run, vaccinated people are much more prone to any mutations in the spike protein, even after they have been infected and cured one or more times.
On the other hand, unvaccinated people will develop permanent, if not permanent, immunity to all strains of the putative virus after being naturally infected with it at least once.

Dans ce dossier, Les Textes de Camara Laye vous pr√©sentent Sophia Stewart, la m√®re de l'≈ìuvre derri√®re les films "Matrix" et "Terminator" dont l'histoire baigne dans cette familiarit√©.

En 1983, une jeune femme noire, Sophia, √©crit une fiction qu'elle intitule „Ää le troisi√®me ≈ìil „Äã, une ≈ìuvre dans laquelle elle se projette dans le futur et d√©crit la destruction de l'humanit√© par les robots et machines (√ßa vous rappelle d√©j√† les films "Terminator" et "Matrix"??). Elle n'aura aucune nouvelle, aucun retour sur sa candidature. Elle oublie tout et la vie continue! Sauf que ....

... Sauf que, en 1999 (plus de 10 ans plus tard), le c√©l√®bre film de science-fiction "Matrix" fait son apparition. Coup de tonnerre et choc infernal : la pauvre Sophia regarde le film et y reconnait son travail, son texte, sa fiction qu'elle avait envoy√©e pour la comp√©tition de 1986.

Le combat fut d'une rudesse sans attribut, une proc√©dure l√©gale qui prendra 14 ans et o√π Sophia n'avait aucune intention d'abandonner. Elle bravera des menaces d'assassinat et des propositions de valises pour retirer sa plainte. 

En Septembre 2014, le verdict tombe et la justice am√©ricaine reconnait enfin Sophia Stewart comme la vraie auteure de l'≈ìuvre „Ää le troisi√®me ≈ìil „Äãqui a servi de ligne d'action pour les films "Matrix" et "Terminator". Elle fut g√©n√©reusement d√©dommag√©e. Bizarrement, la brillante victoire de Sophia ne sera pas publi√©e par les grands journaux pr√©sents durant le long proc√®s.

Les Textes de Camara Laye, le r√©dacteur.', 'The films "Matrix" and "Terminator" were stolen from a black woman! His copyrights are finally recognized!

The sky is blue, the land is majestic and fringed with shimmering sea! But from earth to heaven, how much greed and buried usurpations!!
If you stare at some great inventions of our time, if you can stare at them for a long time without blinking, you will see a black woman or man writhing in pain for misappropriation of his work. In this dossier, Les Textes de Camara Laye introduces you to Sophia Stewart, the mother of the work behind the films "Matrix" and "Terminator" whose history is steeped in this familiarity.

In 1983, a young black woman, Sophia, wrote a fiction that she called „Ääthe third eye„Äã, a work in which she projects herself into the future and describes the destruction of humanity by robots and machines (it reminds you already the films "Terminator" and "Matrix"??). We are in the United States. Sophia is unable to publish her work and puts it away in her drawer. In 1986, three years later, she saw the announcement of a competition inviting submissions of original science fiction texts. Seeing this as an extraordinary opportunity to make her talent known to the world, Sophia takes her manuscript out of the drawer and sends it to the organizers of the competition (the Wachowski filmmaker family). She will have no news, no return on her candidacy. She forgets everything and life goes on! Except that ....

... Except that, in 1999 (more than 10 years later), the famous science fiction film "Matrix" made its appearance. Thunderclap and infernal shock: poor Sophia watches the film and recognizes her work, her text, her fiction that she had sent for the 1986 competition.

The terrible luck for Sophia can be summed up in a small detail: in 1984, she had the good reflex to acquire the copyright on her manuscript. On the strength of this assurance, she immediately seized the FBI of a legal action for theft of her work by denouncing a violation of her copyright. The fight was a tough one without attribute, a legal process that will take 14 years and where Sophia had no intention of giving up. She will brave threats of assassination and proposals for suitcases to withdraw her complaint.

In September 2014, the verdict falls and American justice finally recognizes Sophia Stewart as the true author of the work "the third eye" which served as a line of action for the films "Matrix" and "Terminator". She was generously compensated. Strangely, Sophia's brilliant victory will not be published by the major newspapers present during the long trial.

The Texts of Camara Laye, the editor.', [('fra', 1.0)])

This is the sad story and meaning of black friday. It was during the slave trade in America.

('CRACK IN THE MOON PROVES THE MIRACLE OF PROPHET MUHAMMAD'S; "SPLITTING THE MOON"... READ ON.. THIS IS AMAZING. 

Recent scientific research has confirmed the miracle of Prophet Muhammad (peace be upon him and his holy progeny) regarding ‚ÄúThe Splitting of the Moon‚Äù.

It has been proven through a picture captured by NASA which was published throughout the world. 
The photo from NASA using Apollo 10 and Apollo 11 shows a clear indication (a line) that the Moon was split in past.

The report, spread on scientific foundations in different global parts, said that the picture which illustrates splitting of moon confirms that the moon was split into two halves during its geological age. The report said the scientists were unable to give any scientific explanation for happening of ‚Äòmoon splitting‚Äô as any such splitting was never happened to any heavenly body prior to what happened to the moon. The geologists assert that it is impossible that such a line appears save the moon was split into two halves and then it was rejoined. 

This miracle of the Prophet (peace be upon him) is mentioned in the beginning of Sura Al-Qamar (the moon) about the split of the moon [54:1] ‚ÄòThe Hour has drawn near, and the moon has been cleft asunder (the people of Makkah requested Prophet Muhammad to show them a miracle, so he showed them the splitting of the moon)‚Äô.

Narrated Ibn Masud: During the lifetime of Allah‚Äôs Apostle the moon was split into two parts; one part remained over the mountain, and the other part went beyond the mountain. On that, Allah‚Äôs Apostle said, ‚ÄúWitness this miracle.‚Äù (Bukhari; 60; 387)

As stated one of the greatest miracles of Prophet Muhammad (Peace be upon him) was splitting the moon. This amazing miracle, which couldn‚Äôt be denied even by the unbelievers occurred in the following way:

The miracle of the splitting of the moon occurred before the migration to Medina upon the demands of the polytheists with the permission of Allah and it was shown by the Prophet Muhammad (Peace be upon him) as narrated by many companions like Anas b. Malik, Imam Ali, Huzayfa b. Yaman, Abdullah b. Mas‚Äôud, Abdullah b. Abbas, Abdullah b. Umar, Abdullah b. Amr b. As, Jubayr b. Mut‚Äôim (May Allah be pleased with all of them).

Among Quraish polytheists, Walid b. Mughira, Abu Jahl. As b. Wail, As b. Hisham, Aswad b. Abdi Yaghus, Aswad b. Muttalib, Zama b. Aswad, Nadr b. Harith and others said to the prophet Muhammad (Peace be upon him):
‚ÄúIf you truly are a Prophet that has been appointed by Allah, then split the moon in half. Let it be in such a way that one half will appear over the Mount Abu Qubais and the other half will be seen over Mount Quayqian.‚Äù

The prophet Muhammad (Peace be upon him) asked:

‚ÄúIf I do it, will you become Muslims?‚Äù

The polytheists answered: ‚ÄúYes, we will.‚Äù

It was the 14th night, when it was full moon. The Messenger of Allah stood supplicating to Allah. Allah the Almighty inspired him to sign towards the moon with his finger. When Almighty Allah let the moon split in half, one half standing over Mount Abu Qubais and the other half over Mount Quayqian, the Prophet Muhammad (Peace be upon him) shouted at Muslims:

‚ÄúO Abu Salama b. Abdulasad! Arqam b. Abi‚Äôl Arqam! Bear witness!

And to the polytheists, he said, ‚ÄúBear witness! So and so!

However, the polytheists said ‚ÄúThis is one of the spells of Abu Kabsha‚Äôs Son.‚Äù ‚ÄúThe son of Abu Kabsha cast a spell on you!‚Äù They said ‚ÄúMuhammad cast a spell on us!‚Äù 

Some of them also said:

‚ÄúIf Muhammad had cast a spell on us then, He couldn‚Äôt have cast a spell on everyone! Let us ask the wayfarers who came from the surrounding areas if they saw what we saw.‚Äù

They asked the travelers, who replied:

‚ÄúYes! We also did see the moon in that state! We saw the moon as split! They informed that the moon was split. However, the polytheists, who couldn‚Äôt deny the miracle occurred right in front of their eyes, rejected to be Muslims and to believe by saying: ‚ÄúThis is a prevalent magic!‚Äù, they said ‚ÄúAbu Talib‚Äôs orphan affected the sky with his spell!‚Äù Since they couldn‚Äôt deny the miracle and since they couldn‚Äôt embrace Islam, they had to name it as ‚Äúspell‚Äù.

(Muslim, 8/132 , Ahmad Ibn-i Hanbal, Musnad, 1/447, Ibni Kathir, Tafseer: 4/262, Tirmidhi, 5/398)

Sucedi√≥ antes de que la mayor√≠a de nosotros supi√©ramos lo que estaba sucediendo, incluso antes de que supi√©ramos qu√© era el Coronavirus.

Por otro lado, Corea del Sur / Reino Unido / Italia / Espa√±a y Asia se ven gravemente afectadas.  ¬øY c√≥mo es que Wuhan es repentinamente libre del virus mortal?

 ¬øPor qu√© Beijing no se vio afectado en absoluto?

 Y otro hecho interesante ... el presidente de China, Xi Jinping, visit√≥ a Wuhan en el pico del brote ... ¬øpor qu√© se puso una simple m√°scara facial RM1 para visitar esas √°reas afectadas?  Como presidente, ¬øno deber√≠a haber estado cubierto de pies a cabeza con un traje de materiales peligrosos?  ¬øQuiz√°s porque ya le hab√≠an inyectado el ant√≠doto no hab√≠a necesidad de preocuparse?

 Y China realmente se apodera del mundo.', 'The Coronavirus traveled around the world from Wuhan, but did not reach Beijing or Shanghai...

 China will say that their initial drastic measures they took were very severe and that Wuhan was put on lockdown to contain the spread to other areas. I'm sure they are using the antidote to the virus that was already available before they released it.

As president, shouldn't he have been covered from head to toe in a hazmat suit? Perhaps because he had already been injected with the antidote there was no need to worry?

text:
('*Kementerian Kesihatan memaklumkan kepada orang ramai bahawa influenza kali ini adalah serius. Kaedah pencegahan adalah dengan mengekalkan kerongkong anda dalam keadaan lembap, jangan biarkan kerongkong anda kering. Oleh itu, jangan biarkan anda dahaga kerana sekali membran di kerongkong anda kering, virus akan menyerang tubuh anda dalam masa 10 minit. Minum 50-80cc air suam, 30-50cc untuk kanak-kanak, mengikut umur. Setiap kali anda merasakan tekak anda kering, jangan tunggu, teruskan minum air. Jangan minum banyak pada satu masa kerana ia tidak membantu, sebaliknya minum secara kerap supaya tekak anda lembap. Sehingga akhir Mac, jangan pergi ke tempat-tempat yang sesak, gunakan topeng seperti yang diperlukan terutamanya dalam kereta api atau* *pengangkutan awam. Elakkan makanan goreng atau pedas dan perbanyakkan makanan yang mengandungi vitamin C.*
*Gejala / keterangan adalah*

*1. demam tinggi berulang*
*2 batuk berpanjangan selepas demam*
*3. Kanak-kanak lebih mudah terdedah*
*4. Dewasa biasanya berasa tidak selesa, sakit kepala dan berkaitan dengan pernafasan*
*5: sangat senang berjangkit*

Semoga Allah lindungi anak-anak kita semua dari penyakit ini..', "*The Ministry of Health informs the public that this influenza is serious. The prevention method is to keep your throat moist, don't let your throat dry out. Therefore, don't let yourself be thirsty because once the membrane in your throat is dry, the virus will attack your body within 10 minutes. Drink 50-80cc of warm water, 30-50cc for children, according to age. Whenever you feel your throat dry, don't wait, keep drinking water. Don't drink a lot at one time as it won't help, instead drink regularly to keep your throat moist. Until the end of March, do not go to crowded places, use masks as necessary especially in trains or* *public transport. Avoid fried or spicy foods and eat more foods that contain vitamin C.*
*Symptoms / descriptions are*

*1. recurrent high fever*
*2 prolonged coughs after fever*
*3. Children are more susceptible*
*4. Adults usually feel discomfort, headache and related to breathing*
*5: very contagious*

May God protect all our children from this disease..", [('msa', 1.0)])
